quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  18,102,"Enee, …ìen yeddu…ìe sikku …ìe jogoto jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen gaanin Am, Menen Men heblanii Jahannama on fii yeddu…ìe…ìen wona werde. @Corrected"
  18,103,"Maaku: \"Taw si men hupitay on fii …ìur…ìe hayrude(pertude) golle"
  18,104,Ko …ìen …ìe golle mun yeebii ka ngurdan aduna hara kam…ìe hi…ìe sikka hi…ìe mo∆¥∆¥innde golle
  18,105,"Ko …ìen woni yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen e hawroygol e Makko, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen bone Men √±ii…ìinantaa…ìe √ëalnde Darngal ∆Åetu"
  18,106,"Jahannama ko …óun woni njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe, sabu ko …ìe yeddi kon …ìe jogitii Aayeeje Am …óen e Nulaa…ìe Am …ìen jalkitde"
  18,107,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin laatanto …ìe Aljannaaji Firdawsi Werdi(jipporde)"
  18,108,"Ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe nder ton, …ìe …óa…ì…ìataa gaayi makko waylitorde"
  18,109,"Maaku: \"Sinno maayo ngo laatino ndawa fii Daaluyeeji Joomi am …óin, maayo ngon re'ayno ko adii nde re'ata Daaluyeeji Joomi am …óin, sinno Men addii yeru maggo e …ìeydude"
  18,110,"Maaku: \"Pellet min, ko mi …ìanndinnke yeru mon, no wahayineede e am. Pellet, Rewetee…óo mon On ko Rewetee…óo Gooto, kala jortii…óo hawroyde e Joomi makko yo o gollu golle mo∆¥∆¥e wata o kafidu e dewal Joomi makko hay e gooto"